text: De Eldridge is a really good and easy doctor to communicate with. Thank you so much for receiving my mother and helping her in getting the medicine she needed for her pain.

Always prompt and excellent t service from Dr. Eldridge.
While the new location at Holland Vilkage is convenient the location at Serangoon is much more cosy.
Dr Paveena was very knowledgeable and friendly. She was able to address all my concerns and followed up to check on my progress. Will definitely come to see her again.

I am so pleased to discover this new clinic in the neighbourhood! I had a consultation with Dr Paveena who was very thorough and thoughtful. Staff is also very efficient. Clinic is very nice and clean.
A very pleasant experience. Everyone was kind and very efficient.
